premise_source_doc_sentence: Ji Chang-wook  (  born on July 5 , 1987  )  is a South Korean actor .

He rose to fame playing the leading role of Dong-hae in daily drama series Smile Again  (  2010-2011  )  , and has since starred in Warrior Baek Dong-soo  (  2011  )  , Empress Ki  (  2013-2014  )  , Healer  (  2014-2015  )  , The K2  (  2016  )  , Suspicious Partner  (  2017  )  and the crime-action film Fabricated City  (  2017  )  .
Healer is a 2014-2015 South Korean television series starring Ji Chang-wook , Park Min-young and Yoo Ji-tae .
Though the drama received mediocre ratings in its home country , it gained a fanbase overseas and made Ji Chang-wook known outside Korea .
